  }, {
    "tStartMs": 146955,
    "dDurationMs": 4482,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Well, l. . . Oh, but who is going to look\nafter this place while l'm away?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 151627,
    "dDurationMs": 7116,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "l've got to clean the oven, vacuum the\ncarpets, wash the curtains. . . and then\nthere's ironing to be done."
